# horiseon

Description:
Building a search engine to help user find the right customer for their business. 
All around the world, everyone is dealing business everyday, why not use this 
high tech search engine to make your life easier?

Few things it does:
Online Reputation Management:
- We filter out the outlier online, to give user more accurate review on potential
buisnesses. Some business hire/pay reviewers to write review, our technologies 
can go in and detect those fake reviews and remove them for a more precise and accurate
feedback from the customer.

Social Media Marketing:
- We can filter which Media Marketing would pop up on your site. This will definitely 
helps removing all spammers and scammers marketers. 

Overall with this Search Engine, it will help you finding great buiness, that have great
value, great filter technologies and also it cost effective. 

If you have any question, please feel free to give us a call. 
Or email us. We are gladly to help and answer any questions.
